---
title: Filipino-Inspired Ground Tofu Bowls with Peppers and Snap Peas
description: This family dinner is quick and easy to make, and it's packed with bold flavour. You'll love the crumbled tofu, sugar snap peas and peppers in our sweet and savoury sauce.
